{"url": "https://towardsdatascience.com/customising-vim-to-get-the-best-out-of-it-a5a4dae02562", "time": 1683015294.163933, "path": "towardsdatascience.com/customising-vim-to-get-the-best-out-of-it-a5a4dae02562/", "webpage": {"metadata": {"title": "Customising Vim to Get the Best Out of It | by Shivangi Sareen | Towards Data Science", "h1": "Customising Vim to Get the Best Out of It", "description": "Vim\u2019s commands are such that its entire functionality is achieved using only the keyboard. But it isn\u2019t very easy. It takes a while to pick up and get used to. After all, it\u2019s an editor that all\u2026"}, "outgoing_paragraph_urls": [{"url": "https://towardsdatascience.com/customising-vim-to-get-the-best-out-of-it-part-2-931246996458", "anchor_text": "here", "paragraph_index": 5}], "all_paragraphs": ["Vim\u2019s commands are such that its entire functionality is achieved using only the keyboard. But it isn\u2019t very easy. It takes a while to pick up and get used to. After all, it\u2019s an editor that all kinds of programmers swear by.", "As programmers new to Vim, we often stumble upon it when in the terminal and are completely baffled by the new editing interface and feel totally at loss, beating the keyboard keys to figure out how to take charge of Vim. No wonder \u201cHow to Quit Vim\u201d has been one of the most popular questions in the past on Stack Overflow.", "What\u2019s really important when starting out to use Vim is to create an environment which makes it comfortable for one to use Vim in the first place. Without any of the default settings configured, Vim does not seem attractive one bit and you\u2019re not likely to use Vim at all. Which means you\u2019ll end up missing out on this extremely powerful modal editor, which is a huge loss as a programmer.", "Vim is highly customisable and it\u2019s supposed to aid you in editing; not the opposite. So, let\u2019s get right into some of the settings to make Vim feel right at home.", "Add these setting to your .vimrc file and notice the difference! You\u2019ll surely find editing text in Vim a lot more appealing now!", "Check out some much needed additions in part 2 here!", "Your home for data science. A Medium publication sharing concepts, ideas and codes.", "Software Engineer @Apple | Reader | Writer | The Sustainable Edit"], "all_outgoing_urls": [{"url": "https://rsci.app.link/?%24canonical_url=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fp%2Fa5a4dae02562&%7Efeature=LoOpenInAppButton&%7Echannel=ShowPostUnderCollection&source=---two_column_layout_nav----------------------------------", "anchor_text": "Open in app"}, {"url": "https://medium.com/m/signin?operation=register&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Ftowardsdatascience.com%2Fcustomising-vim-to-get-the-best-out-of-it-a5a4dae02562&source=post_page---two_column_layout_nav-----------------------global_nav-----------", "anchor_text": "Sign up"}, {"url": "https://medium.com/m/signin?operation=login&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Ftowardsdatascience.com%2Fcustomising-vim-to-get-the-best-out-of-it-a5a4dae02562&source=post_page---two_column_layout_nav-----------------------global_nav-----------", "anchor_text": "Sign In"}, {"url": "https://medium.com/?source=---two_column_layout_nav----------------------------------", "anchor_text": ""}, {"url": "https://medium.com/m/signin?operation=register&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fnew-story&source=---two_column_layout_nav-----------------------new_post_sidenav-----------", "anchor_text": "Write"}, {"url": "https://medium.com/search?source=---two_column_layout_nav----------------------------------", "anchor_text": ""}, {"url": "https://medium.com/m/signin?operation=register&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Ftowardsdatascience.com%2Fcustomising-vim-to-get-the-best-out-of-it-a5a4dae02562&source=post_page---two_column_layout_nav-----------------------global_nav-----------", "anchor_text": "Sign up"}, {"url": "https://medium.com/m/signin?operation=login&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Ftowardsdatascience.com%2Fcustomising-vim-